title: Instinct Boot
description:
The Fox Instinct Boot, Engineered to set the Performance Standard

Features: 5 Patented Comfort Components That Consist of:
-An Athletic Insole.
-A Poly-Urethane Mid-Sole w/ Embedded Steel Shank.
-TPU Heal Stabilizer for Support.
-And AN Exclusive Duratac Outsole & Burn Guard Built From A Fox Proprietary Compound, Provides Unmatched Grip & Durability.
-The Patented Buckle System Utilizes a Ball Socket Design and Provides Effortless Fluidity as the Boot Flexes.
-Patented Hinge Lockout, which Stops Motion Before Hyper Extension, Provides Fluid Movement with Zero Break-in Time Required.
-RCI or Ride Control Interface Provides Excellent Connectivity to the Bike.
-And named Product of the Year by Transworld MX & Dirt Rider magazines.
